%Steps%

During this step, we're going to set the run to jump start transition.

1.	Return to the **Arms State Machine** graph and drag a wire from the **Run** state to the **JumpStart** state.

	![](RuntoJumpStart.png)

1.	Double-click the transition to edit it.

1.	Control-click on **IsFalling** in the **My Blueprint** tab and drag into the graph to create a **Get Is Falling** node.

1.	Connect the output Boolean pin from the **Get Is Falling** node to the input Boolean **Can Enter Transition** pin on the **Result** node.

	![](IsFallingtoResult.png)

